.TH "vcc_probe" 9 "vcc_probe" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vcc_probe \- Initialize VCC port
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vcc_probe
.BI "(struct vio_dev *vdev "  ","
.BI "const struct vio_device_id *id "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "vdev" 12
Pointer to VIO device of the new VCC port
.IP "id" 12
VIO device ID
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes a VCC port to receive serial console data from
the guest domain. Sets up a TTY end point on the control
domain. Sets up VIO/LDC link between the guest & control
domain endpoints.
.SH "RETURN"
status of the probe
